column1: IF ccr_zoa_dhe_d is MF 0 AND ccr_zob_dhe_d is MF 0 AND ccr_a_cortolone_d is MF 1 THEN 4_Obese is MF 1 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 1 AND 2_Normal is MF 1
IF ccr_thf_d is MF 0 AND ccr_etio_d is MF 2 THEN 3_Surpoid is MF 0
IF ccr_a_cortolone_d is MF 0 THEN 4_Obese is MF 0 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0 AND 2_Normal is MF 1 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 1
IF ccr_s_pt_d is MF 2 AND ccr_zob_dhe_d is MF 0 AND ccr_thaldo_d is MF 2 THEN 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0
IF ccr_pt_d is MF 1 AND ccr_s_ad_17b_d is MF 2 THEN 3_Surpoid is MF 0 AND 4_Obese is MF 1
ELSE : 1_SousPoid is 0  2_Normal is 0  3_Surpoid is 0  4_Obese is 0  5_ExtremeObese is 1
